[]\T1/lmtt/m/n/10 ## GSM4622627 A total of 86 RNA-seq libraries generated above were pooled and sequenced on a NovaSeq 6000 Sequencing System (Illumina) in a pair-ended fasion (2 x 100 cycles). 41 M to 124 M paired-end reads were obtained for each sample. FastQ files were used as input for RNA-Seq data processing. Library prep and sequencing were performed at TBseq (Palo Alto, CA).[] 
 []


